WITH current_period AS (
    SELECT 
        CAMPAIGN_TYPE AS type,
        SUM(SPEND) as spend,
        SUM(SIGN_UPS) as su,
        SUM(QUALIFIED_SIGN_UPS) as qsu,
        SUM(PAYWALL) as pwc
    FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.MART_GOOGLE_ADS_PERFORMANCE
    WHERE {{# mart_google_ads_performance.date.filter }} DATE {{/ mart_google_ads_performance.date.filter }}
      AND CAMPAIGN_TYPE IN ('Brand', 'Non-Brand')
    GROUP BY CAMPAIGN_TYPE
),

calculated AS (
    SELECT 
        type,
        ROUND(spend, 2) as spend,
        ROUND(su) as su,
        ROUND(spend / NULLIF(su, 0), 2) as cpsu,
        ROUND(qsu) as qsu,
        ROUND(spend / NULLIF(qsu, 0), 2) as cpqsu,
        ROUND(100.0 * qsu / NULLIF(su, 0), 1) as qsu_share,
        ROUND(pwc) as pwc,
        ROUND(spend / NULLIF(pwc, 0), 2) as cppc,
        ROUND(100.0 * pwc / NULLIF(su, 0), 1) as paywall_rate
    FROM current_period
)

SELECT * FROM calculated

UNION ALL

SELECT 
    'Total' as type,
    ROUND(SUM(spend), 2),
    ROUND(SUM(su)),
    ROUND(SUM(spend) / NULLIF(SUM(su), 0), 2),
    ROUND(SUM(qsu)),
    ROUND(SUM(spend) / NULLIF(SUM(qsu), 0), 2),
    ROUND(100.0 * SUM(qsu) / NULLIF(SUM(su), 0), 1),
    ROUND(SUM(pwc)),
    ROUND(SUM(spend) / NULLIF(SUM(pwc), 0), 2),
    ROUND(100.0 * SUM(pwc) / NULLIF(SUM(su), 0), 1)
FROM calculated

ORDER BY 
    CASE WHEN type = 'Total' THEN 2 WHEN type = 'Brand' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END

WITH metrics AS (
    SELECT
        SUM(SPEND) as total_spend,
        SUM(PAYWALL) as total_pwc
    FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.MART_GOOGLE_ADS_PERFORMANCE
    WHERE {{# mart_google_ads_performance.date.filter }} DATE {{/ mart_google_ads_performance.date.filter }}
      AND CAMPAIGN_TYPE IN ('Brand', 'Non-Brand')
)
SELECT
    '$' || ROUND(total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0), 0) as "display_value",
    '$400' as "max_display",
    '$177' as "target_display",
    CASE
        WHEN total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0) <= 177 THEN 'rgb(34, 197, 94)'
        WHEN total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0) <= 220 THEN 'rgb(234, 179, 8)'
        ELSE 'rgb(239, 68, 68)'
    END as "fill_color",
    CASE
        WHEN total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0) <= 177 THEN 'On Target ✓'
        WHEN total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0) <= 220 THEN 'Watch'
        ELSE 'Over Target'
    END as "status",
    'conic-gradient(from -90deg, ' || 
    CASE
        WHEN total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0) <= 177 THEN 'rgb(34, 197, 94)'
        WHEN total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0) <= 220 THEN 'rgb(234, 179, 8)'
        ELSE 'rgb(239, 68, 68)'
    END || ' ' ||
    ROUND(LEAST(1, GREATEST(0, (total_spend / NULLIF(total_pwc, 0)) / 400)) * 180, 1) || 
    'deg, transparent 0)' as "gradient"
FROM metrics

measures.label: High Level Performance Brand Vs Non Brand Count

raw_sql_select.sql:
SELECT
    campaign_type AS type,
    SUM(spend) AS spend,
    SUM(sign_ups) AS su,
    CASE WHEN SUM(sign_ups) > 0 THEN SUM(spend) / SUM(sign_ups) ELSE NULL END AS cpsu,
    SUM(qualified_sign_ups) AS qsu,
    CASE WHEN SUM(qualified_sign_ups) > 0 THEN SUM(spend) / SUM(qualified_sign_ups) ELSE NULL END AS cpqsu,
    CASE WHEN SUM(sign_ups) > 0 THEN SUM(qualified_sign_ups) / SUM(sign_ups) ELSE NULL END AS qsu_share,
    SUM(paywall) AS pwc,
    CASE WHEN SUM(paywall) > 0 THEN SUM(spend) / SUM(paywall) ELSE NULL END AS cppc,
    CASE WHEN SUM(sign_ups) > 0 THEN SUM(paywall) / SUM(sign_ups) ELSE NULL END AS paywall_rate
FROM training_database.public.mart_google_ads_performance
WHERE date >= '2026-01-22' AND date <= '2026-01-28'
  AND campaign_type IN ('Brand', 'Non-Brand')
GROUP BY campaign_type
ORDER BY campaign_type
